		TREATAS({"Credit Card"}, 'ecommerce_sales'[payment_method])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Beauty"}, 'ecommerce_sales'[category])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		TREATAS({"New Brunswick"}, 'ecommerce_sales'[region])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'ecommerce_sales'[category],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			"Net_Sale", 'ecommerce_sales'[Net Sale],
			"ecommerce_salesNet_Sale", IGNORE(CALCULATE('ecommerce_sales'[Net Sale], KEEPFILTERS(__H0FilterTable)))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [Net_Sale], 0, 'ecommerce_sales'[category], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[Net_Sale] DESC, 'ecommerce_sales'[category]
